{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":5170,"text":"Recently, I flew over a crowd"},{"time":7521,"text":"of thousands of people in Brazil"},{"time":9906,"text":"playing music by George Frideric Handel."},{"time":13539,"text":"I also drove along the streets of Amsterdam,"},{"time":16543,"text":"again playing music by this same composer."},{"time":19918,"text":"Let's take a look."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22685,"text":"(Music: George Frideric Handel, \"Allegro.\"\nPerformed by Daria van den Bercken.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41888,"text":"(Video) Daria van den Bercken: I\nlive there on the third floor."},{"time":43960,"text":"(In Dutch) I live there on the corner."},{"time":45849,"text":"I actually live there, around the corner."},{"time":47457,"text":"and you'd be really welcome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49133,"text":"Man: (In Dutch) Does that sound like fun?\nChild: (In Dutch) Yes!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51952,"text":"[(In Dutch) \"Handel house concert\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76722,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":88236,"text":"Daria van den Bercken: All this was a real"},{"time":90154,"text":"magical experience for hundreds of reasons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93810,"text":"Now you may ask, why have I done these things?"},{"time":96330,"text":"They're not really typical for a musician's"},{"time":98692,"text":"day-to-day life."},{"time":100913,"text":"Well, I did it because I fell in love with the music"},{"time":104463,"text":"and I wanted to share it with as many people"},{"time":107545,"text":"as possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109829,"text":"It started a couple of years ago."},{"time":111944,"text":"I was sitting at home on the couch with the flu"},{"time":115375,"text":"and browsing the Internet a little,"},{"time":117497,"text":"when I found out that Handel had written works"},{"time":120320,"text":"for the keyboard."},{"time":122320,"text":"Well, I was surprised. I did not know this."},{"time":124637,"text":"So I downloaded the sheet music and started playing."},{"time":129020,"text":"And what happened next was"},{"time":130920,"text":"that I entered this state of pure,"},{"time":134491,"text":"unprejudiced amazement."},{"time":137360,"text":"It was an experience"},{"time":139700,"text":"of being totally in awe of the music,"},{"time":142827,"text":"and I had not felt that in a long time."},{"time":146607,"text":"It might be easier to relate to this when you hear it."},{"time":150760,"text":"The first piece that I played through"},{"time":154051,"text":"started like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157845,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182950,"text":"Well this sounds very melancholic, doesn't it?"},{"time":186680,"text":"And I turned the page and what came next"},{"time":189714,"text":"was this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191672,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218624,"text":"Well, this sounds very energetic, doesn't it?"},{"time":222690,"text":"So within a couple of minutes,"},{"time":225390,"text":"and the piece isn't even finished yet,"},{"time":227550,"text":"I experienced two very contrasting characters:"},{"time":231645,"text":"beautiful melancholy and sheer energy."},{"time":235267,"text":"And I consider these two elements to be"},{"time":237337,"text":"vital human expressions."},{"time":240140,"text":"And the purity of the music makes you hear it"},{"time":242815,"text":"very effectively."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247893,"text":"I've given a lot of children's concerts"},{"time":250233,"text":"for children of seven and eight years old,"},{"time":253371,"text":"and whatever I play, whether it's Bach, Beethoven,"},{"time":257185,"text":"even Stockhausen,"},{"time":258760,"text":"or some jazzy music,"},{"time":261752,"text":"they are open to hear it,"},{"time":263901,"text":"really willing to listen,"},{"time":265188,"text":"and they are comfortable doing so."},{"time":268716,"text":"And when classes come in"},{"time":270250,"text":"with children who are just a few years older,"},{"time":273699,"text":"11, 12, I felt that I sometimes already had trouble"},{"time":278547,"text":"in reaching them like that."},{"time":280640,"text":"The complexity of the music does become an issue,"},{"time":284307,"text":"and actually the opinions of others —"},{"time":288140,"text":"parents, friends, media — they start to count."},{"time":292823,"text":"But the young ones, they don't question"},{"time":295331,"text":"their own opinion."},{"time":298672,"text":"They are in this constant state of wonder,"},{"time":301664,"text":"and I do firmly believe that we can keep listening"},{"time":305354,"text":"like these seven-year-old children,"},{"time":307638,"text":"even when growing up."},{"time":310112,"text":"And that is why I have played"},{"time":312261,"text":"not only in the concert hall"},{"time":314601,"text":"but also on the street, online, in the air:"},{"time":318930,"text":"to feel that state of wonder,"},{"time":321497,"text":"to truly listen,"},{"time":323679,"text":"and to listen without prejudice."},{"time":327223,"text":"And I would like to invite you"},{"time":329349,"text":"to do so now."},{"time":338862,"text":"(Music: George Frideric Handel, \"Chaconne in G Major.\"\nPerformed by Daria van den Bercken.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":545733,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":551960,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":553906,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}